      "content": "that's really helpful for the students' prep. to round out their understanding, though, i'd like to see how you'd handle the counter-arguments. what are the most common criticisms people level against this view of sovereignty and the rule of law in the context of immigration? i want to make sure they aren't blindsided by the typical rebuttals they'll face in the round.",
